  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study carry out is to determine whether the use of oral pregabalin premedication to
      assess the analgesic efficacy, opiod sparing, adverse effect and clinical value in
      post-operative pain management.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
